author: Leslie Thomas, 252 Foods LLC
title: Leslie Thomas, 252 Foods LLC
text: We're a food startup, and came to StandUpPouches.net after a lot of research. We crossed our fingers and hoped for the best. From start to finish, the process was great. We now have packaging that meets and even exceeds our expectations. Deadlines were met and the price was right. Thanks for your excellent work!
